{"tid":2148621,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【港版國安法】國安處警司李桂華稱編採部不能搜 在場警員反口趕記者離開座位","createTime":"2020-08-10T04:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T04:46:06.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"067556bf92a1166f4a8d37f5b4fa1e145b13c7b3","tid":2148621,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T04:29:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200810/7YJWD3FDRB5J2SACBRDMA4PHJM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200810%2F7YJWD3FDRB5J2SACBRDMA4PHJM%2F&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25YpLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=1e19bd19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200810%2F7YJWD3FDRB5J2SACBRDMA4PHJM%2F&h=8775a3c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200810/7YJWD3FDRB5J2SACBRDMA4PHJM/</a><br />\n<br />\n今日（10日）清晨，警方以《壹傳媒》創辦人黎智英涉嫌違反《國安法》罪名將其拘捕，當中涉及被捕人數達7名，包括多名《蘋果日報》高層，其後近200名警員進入《蘋果》大樓，黎智英雙手反綁被警方帶到其辦公室。警方國家安全處高級警司李桂華指出，今早警員已向負責人展示手令，由於搜查地點為傳媒機構，擔心牽涉新聞材料，李稱已與警司作初步審查，指出部分區域如編採部不能搜，但警方在《蘋果》的封鎖線卻無限擴大，甚至原本在編採部工作的記者亦突然被要求離開座位，即使表示正在進行新聞工作仍被要求離開，與李桂華説法大相徑庭。"},{"pid":"c6a0f53525f02771d1acb7806e9679f6ce226eef","tid":2148621,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T04:31:06.000Z","msg":"警謊"},{"pid":"202e706873745945f896c037c2f51607c4295fbb","tid":2148621,"uid":307203,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T04:31:43.000Z","msg":"任何刑事案件，只要見李桂華有份出現，你就知道，這件案件必會變為業餘、不認真，和像馬戲團。"},{"pid":"fb59c99bebb2e58048a793bfb5a58abf8cbaa236","tid":2148621,"uid":335434,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T04:31:44.000Z","msg":"其實無第二個肯帶隊咩? 次次都搵佢搞場業餘馬戲團式搜證當做咗嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9be8a44e4221b06ac7d671c36b04065e4adb6c","tid":2148621,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote"